---
// Problem Section - Agitate the gap
---

<section id="the-problem" class="relative py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 border-t border-brand-gray overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-dark"></div>
  <!-- Dashboard image - centered -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
    <div class="w-auto h-full aspect-video bg-[url('/images/dashboards-bg.svg')] bg-contain bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-[0.08]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-container relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-text mb-8">
        Your business has dashboards. Your body has nothing.
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-brand-muted">
        <p>
          You've got systems for everything. Revenue tracking. Project management. Team accountability.
        </p>

        <p>
          But your health? You're winging it. Eating whatever's available. Training when you "have time" (so... never). Telling yourself you'll sort it when things calm down.
        </p>

        <p class="text-brand-text font-semibold">
          Things won't calm down. Business isn't designed to.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
